Hello <%= @newsletter.first_name %>!
This weekend Marin Cricket Club has <%= @upcoming.count %> games on!

<% if @mno.blank? %>
Marin One
Marin One are on a bye, they are probably mowing the lawn, walking the dog or finally writing that novel.
<% else %>
<% @mno.each do |mno| %>
Marin One
<% if mno.home_team.name === 'Marin One' %>
Playing against <%= mno.away_team.name %> on <%= mno.date.strftime('%A, %B %d') %> at Piper Park, Larkspur.
<% else %>
Playing against <%= mno.home_team.name %> on <%= mno.date.strftime('%A, %B %d') %> at <%= mno.home_team.home_field %>.
<% end %>
First ball is at <%= mno.start_time.strftime('%H:%M %P') %> so get down and support our boys if you can!
Copy and paste this link into your browser for more information:
<%= schedule_url(mno) %>
<% end %>
<% end %>


